parameters:
"This toilet seems to be out of order. It looks like the
water pipes are deteriorating and about to break."

"That's it, water! I just need to make everyone here believe
that the basement is flooding!"

(If I break these water pipes and let a flood of water into
the hallway, anyone would believe that rainwater is seeping
in!)

(I remember seeing on the news that if a basement gets
flooded, you can't get out.)

(If the basement floods, everyone will flee from here. Then,
surely Makoto will be freed from this place!)

"Alright, let's break these water pipes right away! I need
to prepare some tools first!"

"Alright... Let's try to break this water pipe with the
tools from the toolbox I picked up earlier."
"I did it! The water pipe is broken... Whoaahhhhhhhhhhh!"

"Woah, the water is gushing out with such force! So this is
what happens when a water pipe breaks!"

"I need to get away from here quickly... Makoto... please,
make it out safely...!"
